										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Pawn to Don Mafia Crime Story delivers a dramatic journey that combines choice-based simulation with suffocating survival pressure. Your moral courage will be clearly revealed in the toughest situations. As a desperate father, you only have 30 days to gather $100,000 for your child’s bone marrow transplant. In this journey, you truly resort to any means to collect enough money. As a result, your child may live, but you will turn yourself into a ruthless crime boss.</p>
<h3>CHOICE-DRIVEN GAMEPLAY &amp; MONEY MAKING</h3>
<p>Every decision you make directly affects the rise, fall, and fate of your entire family. In this high-pressure race for money, there is no room for mercy. Showing leniency to enemies is the same as condemning your own child. Desperation will push you into harsh choices. As such, the line between good and evil becomes thinner than ever. Whether you can obtain that amount of money ultimately depends on your own hands.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Diverse income sources</strong>: Take office jobs, gamble, or build a criminal empire.</li>
<li><strong>Life-or-death decisions</strong>: Every choice leads to different outcomes for your journey.</li>
<li><strong>Time pressure</strong>: Race against a brutal schedule to accumulate wealth before it’s too late.</li>
</ul>
<h3>MORAL DILEMMAS &amp; SACRIFICE</h3>
<p>The game puts you in difficult ethical situations. The price of power and money can be your conscience. You must weigh everything to save your child on the brink of death. The journey from nothing to controlling fate is a chain of haunting sacrifices. The wealth in your hands may be built on the blood of your enemies.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Test of humanity</strong>: Face cruel choices to protect the one you love most.</li>
<li><strong>Rise and fall system</strong>: Experience character transformation based on your chosen path.</li>
<li><strong>The cost of power</strong>: Fully realize the sacrifices required to achieve success.</li>
</ul>
