										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Because the universe is vast, there may be many mysteries that we have yet to discover. There are many planets in the universe, each with its resources. Join Idle Planet Miner; you will directly exploit the resources available in the universe.</p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-77184" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-2-500x889.jpg" alt="Idle Planet Miner" width="500" height="889" srcset="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-2-500x889.jpg 500w, https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-2.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></td>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-77185" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-3-500x889.jpg" alt="Idle Planet Miner" width="500" height="889" srcset="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-3-500x889.jpg 500w, https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-3.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>BECOME A MINING ENGINEER</h2>
<p>If you come to Idle Planet Miner, you and your lovely assistant Luna will be transported to other planets than Earth to work as a resource mining engineer. Luna has tasked you with piloting a ship that mines the planet for precious metals and minerals. You and your ship will travel into space at the start of the game. There may be many undiscovered planets in this region of space. If you click on each planet, you&#8217;ll see detailed information, and it&#8217;s clear what resources these planets contain. You will land your ship on these planets to maximize profits and immediately set up mining and mineral production centers.</p>
<h2>GREAT ADVENTURE</h2>
<p>If you want to start mining right away in Idle Planet Miner, you will need to spend some money, just like in the real world. While working in the mines, you can watch the expansion of your galaxy. There will be many opportunities to complete unique goals and get valuable rewards. For example, assigning a manager of 1 planet can earn 20 purple orbs. Natural phenomena will occur throughout the game, but you must keep them from distracting you to the point of losing your aim.</p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-77186" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-4-500x889.jpg" alt="Idle Planet Miner" width="500" height="889" srcset="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-4-500x889.jpg 500w, https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-4.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></td>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-77187" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-5-500x889.jpg" alt="Idle Planet Miner" width="500" height="889" srcset="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-5-500x889.jpg 500w, https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-5.jpg 900w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>UPGRADES FOR MINING SHIPS</h2>
<p>Mining more ore is necessary if you want to keep up with the growing world demand; otherwise, you will not be able to meet the needs of the galaxy. As a result, your income and profits will increase. You will need to upgrade your mining equipment as the amount of ore you mine from a planet increases. You can increase the amount of ore your ship can transport. Each planet will have three factors to consider to upgrade: mining output, shipping speed, and cargo capacity. The higher these factors, the more ore will be mined, and the speed of the ship will increase accordingly.</p>
<h2>BECOME A BOSS</h2>
<p>However, you will need to spend a certain amount and wait for a planet to become available before you can start mining. Your workload will skyrocket once you unlock new planets. When this happens, you should hire more people, including managers, to reduce the amount of manual labor required while increasing productivity and profits. While legally changing someone&#8217;s last name is difficult in real life, you have full control over the names assigned to the manager and other characters in Idle Planet Miner. It would be best if you gave your managers names that are simple and easy to remember.</p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-77188 size-medium" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-6-500x889.jpg" alt="Idle Planet Miner" width="500" height="889" srcset="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-6-500x889.jpg 500w, https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner-6.jpg 900w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></td>
<td style="width: 50%;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-82740" src="https://MOD HURU.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/idle-planet-miner.png" alt="" width="500" height="889" /></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>CRAFTING ITEMS</h2>
<p>You must think like a business person when playing the game because you cannot indefinitely leave the ore you mined in the storage area. For example, to create copper bars, it is necessary to smelt thousands of different copper ores after all the required resources have been extracted from the ground. When you put something in the oven, it will start melting to create new things, regardless of whether you use it. Those who take this approach have a better chance of completing the task promptly.</p>
