										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Blend It 3D is a relaxing game with some ASMR elements blending fruits to create delicious smoothies following countless orders. The game also lets you operate a smoothie stand at the beach, so expect a surge of smoothie orders and earn endless revenue as you sell the best smoothie out there.</p>
<h2>START YOUR FIRST SMOOTHIE STAND WITH COUNTLESS CUSTOMERS</h2>
<p>In this game, you&#8217;ll be transported to a tropical island and put in charge of a beachside bar, where you&#8217;ll offer a wide variety of clients tasty (and sometimes frightening) beverages made from exotic ingredients while also keeping up with their orders and making sure they&#8217;re properly decorated. The gameplay is filled with exotic, wholesome fun for people of all ages, thanks to its heady mix of culinary, design, and restaurant management with a sprinkling of bizarre humor.</p>
<h2>COMPLETE THE ORDERS TO PROGRESS FURTHER</h2>
<p>Tap the screen to mix like a pro, and you can do it with many tasty foods and even more unusual substances. You&#8217;ll have to time your blend to ensure you achieve the appropriate recipes based on the customer&#8217;s requirement, as each component in the game has a different consistency and blending speed. New recipes and customers will show up later in the gameplay, and they sometimes have crazy ideas for new smoothies, and you must follow them to earn extra hefty money for your services.</p>
<h2>UPGRADE YOUR BAR WITH NEW EQUIPMENT</h2>
<p>Use your prizes to remodel your bar to resemble a luxurious tropical resort instead of a rundown shack. Keep even more customers satisfied and continue blending to your heart&#8217;s delight by upgrading your business with additional equipment, glassware, decorations, and ingredients. The more you upgrade the bar, the better it will be in producing smoothies. That will lessen some of the customer stress or pressure as you keep up with the orders.</p>
