<p>At its core, Drift Runner delivers unrivaled customization for creating your ultimate bespoke drift build. Fine-tune suspension geometries like camber and height to optimize handling. Swap engines and turbocharge for maximum power. Equip widebody kits, bumpers, side skirts, exhausts, spoilers and customize aesthetics with thousands of color and wheel options. Building allows personalized drift machines tailored to your style from visual flair to performance. Take a classic JDM ride and give it your signature look.</p>
<p>The game captures the worldwide drifting scene through authentic global track and location modeling. Tear up perilous Touge mountain passes in Japan. Scream around indoor courses like those found in the UK and Russia Drift Series. Compete for glory on licensed pro circuits modeled off their real-world counterparts from the Formula Drift series. Actual drift zone roads and championships let you experience drifting culture across the globe.</p>
<p>Intuitive drifting physics cater to both amateurs learning the fundamentals of clutch kicking, handbrake turns and other techniques as well as experts executing advanced methods like clutch kick initiations and long continuous drift chaining. Smoothly transition from basic to expert controls as your skills improve. The driving accommodates casual fans and diehard enthusiasts alike.</p>
<p>Complementing single player career mode, online multiplayer battles enable competing against drifting rivals from around the globe to prove your talents in head-to-head tandems and battles. Rise up leaderboards tracking mastery and overall status in the worldwide Drift Runner community. The seamless online integration and rankings foster a competitive social environment.</p>
<p>With incredibly deep car customization, real-world drift locations, accessible yet realistic physics and integrated multiplayer competition, Drift Runner stands as the definitive drifting simulation, built by gearheads and drifting fans for gearheads and drifting fans. Live out tuning and competitive driving dreams in one incredible package.</p>
